{\displaystyle C_{V}={\frac {\partial U}{\partial T}}=3N{\frac {(\hbar \omega )^{2}}{k_{B}T^{2}}}{\frac {e^{\hbar \omega /k_{B}T}}{(e^{\hbar \omega /k_{B}T}-1)^{2}}}\,\!}

